    <h2>License &amp; Compliance Costs for Restaurants in India</h2>
    <p>Licensing is not optional — it's the foundation that keeps your restaurant legally operational. An unlicensed restaurant risks closure, fines, and reputational damage. The good news: total licensing costs are a small fraction of the overall setup budget. Here's every license you need and what each costs in 2026:</p>
